nodes.text: Vice-President in charge of Corporate Security

Vice-President in charge of Corporate Security was the title given to the Viceprex who oversaw the Corporate Sector Authority's Security Division, as well as the Stars' End prison on Mytus VII. In 2 BBY this title was held by Mirkovig Hirken. He was slain during the Liberation of Stars' End. After his death, Assistant-Deputy Viceprex Ilm Vaz-Weplinn was given the position by the Executive Directorship Board.
